    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieved required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at this risk level. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as sufficiently credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the evidence package supports regulatory submission for a Class II device.",
